data.description: Step into a home that exudes timeless charm! The spacious living room featuring a gas log fireplace, seamlessly connects to the formal dining room, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere for entertaining. The kitchen is equipped w/modern amenities & a cozy breakfast area. From the kitchen, step into a sunroom that overlooks the inviting in-ground pool and private backyard, providing a perfect setting for relaxation. Venture downstairs to discover a full basement w/endless possibilities. Whether you envision a large recreation room, a cozy family room, or a functional workshop, the space awaits your creative touch. With three bedrooms & three full baths, this home offers both comfort & convenience. The three-car garage ensures ample space for your vehicles & storage needs. Situated on a large lot, this property is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. The proximity to the golf course adds an extra layer of appeal, making this classic ranch a truly special find. Don't miss this opportunity!
